These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, lemonade, sprite, water
The people have 4 different jobs:  pilot, accountant, writer, journalist
1. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
2. the journalist is on the left or right of the pilot##3
3. the pilot is in an odd position##4
4. the person drinking water is somewhere to the left of the journalist##5
5. the pilot is the person drinking lemonade##1
6. the person drinking sprite is the accountant##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Beverage      | water  | hot-chocolate | lemonade  | sprite |
| Job   | writer | journalist      | pilot | accountant |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-2::.
4 different games are played: scrabble, chess, mah-jongg, whist
4 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, goat, horse
1. the person playing chess is between the owner of the bird and the owner of the horse##2
2. the person playing whist is somewhere to the left of the owner of the horse##5
3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
4. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person playing whist##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Game   | whist | mah-jongg | chess   | scrabble |
| Pet           | goat      | bird    | chinchilla | horse      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-3::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, corn, peach, potato
House: cape-cod, colonial, craftsman, cottage
1. the person eating corn is the colonial house##1
2. the cottage house is on the right of the person eating corn##1
3. the craftsman house is somewhere to the left of the cape-cod house##5
4. the cape-cod house is on the left or right of the person eating peach##3
5. the person eating potato is somewhere to the right of the cottage house##5
6. the person eating corn is somewhere to the left of the craftsman house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2    |     3     |   4    |
| Food        | corn | cabbage | peach     | potato |
| House   | colonial  | cottage   | craftsman | cape-cod    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, singing, skydiving, woodworking
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, soul, funk, pop
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the right of the fan of funk##5
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the fan of pop and the fan of soul##2
4. the fan of funk is on the left or right of the fan of pop##3
5. the fan of pop is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | skydiving | card-games | singing | woodworking |
| Music-Genre   | pop   | funk     | soul    | house       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, hot-chocolate, lemonade, tea
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, mystery, western, zombie
1. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the left of the person watching disaster movies##5
2. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
3. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the left of the person drinking mirinda##5
4. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
5. the person watching disaster movies is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
6. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage          | lemonade | tea   | mirinda   | hot-chocolate    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery  | zombie | disaster | western |

