2. the fan of country is somewhere to the left of the turkish##5
3. the turkish is between the fan of jazz and the thai##2
4. the fan of classical is on the right of the japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |       3        |     4     |
| Music-Genre           | country | reggae | jazz | classical |
| Nationality   | thai        | turkish     | japanese       | russian   |

