.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-7::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, davidoff, chaman, oliveros
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, hamster, snake, turtle
1. the owner of the hamster is the oliveros-smoker##1
2. the blend-smoker is between the davidoff-smoker and the owner of the snake##2
3. the owner of the goldfish is in an even position##4
4. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the left of the blend-smoker##5
5. the blend-smoker is in an even position##4
6. the chaman-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Cigar   | davidoff | blend  | chaman  | oliveros   |
| Pet           | turtle  | goldfish | snake | hamster |

