.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-8::.
There 4 different types of food: carrot, mango, pear, strawberry
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, rock-climbing, filmmaking, chess
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
2. the person eating strawberry is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##5
3. the person eating strawberry is on the left or right of the person eating pear##3
4. the person eating mango is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
5. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Food   | mango     | strawberry | pear     | carrot   |
| Hobby    | chess | rock-climbing  | filmmaking | traveling |

