.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-9::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, iced-tea, milk
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, march, january, may
1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
4. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in may##5
5. the person who's birthday is in march is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in june##5
6. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in january##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |   3    |  4   |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | iced-tea | milk   | cola |
| Birthday       | june       | january   | may | march |

