.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, iced-tea, mirinda, tea
City: miami, prague, edinburgh, rome
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person traveling to prague##3
2. the person traveling to miami is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5
3. the person traveling to rome is somewhere to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##5
4. the person traveling to miami is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to rome##5
5. the person traveling to prague is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |   3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | mirinda       | cola   | tea        |
| City      | prague  | rome | miami | edinburgh |

