1. the havana-smoker is somewhere to the right of the canadian##5
2. the chaman-smoker is somewhere to the right of the american##5
3. the brazilian is on the left of the mexican##1
4. the mexican is the chaman-smoker##1
5. the vegafina-smoker is somewhere to the right of the havana-smoker##5
6. the brazilian is on the left or right of the american##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3      |    4     |
| Cigar   | ritmeester  | havana | vegafina | chaman |
| Nationality   | canadian | american | brazilian   | mexican  |

