.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-15::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: orange, ebony, purple, aquamarine
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, entrepreneur, manager, mechanic
1. the person who likes aquamarine is between the person who likes purple and the person who likes ebony##2
2. the analyst is on the left or right of the person who likes aquamarine##3
3. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1
4. the person who likes purple is somewhere to the right of the manager##5
5. the manager is somewhere to the left of the mechanic##5
6. the manager is on the left of the mechanic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |      3       |     4     |
| Color   | orange | purple  | aquamarine      | ebony |
| Job     | manager    | mechanic | entrepreneur | analyst   |

