The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, electronic, gospel, hip-hop
1. the nigerian is in an even position##4
2. the turkish is on the far left or far right##3
3. the mexican is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
4. the fan of classical is in an even position##4
5. the colombian is somewhere to the left of the turkish##5
6. the nigerian is between the colombian and the fan of electronic##2
7. the mexican is somewhere to the right of the colombian##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |
| Nationality      | colombian   | nigerian  | mexican      | turkish       |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | hip-hop | electronic | classical |

