.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-17::.
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, hamster, goldfish, fish
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, helicopter, taxi, tram
1. the owner of the fish is somewhere to the left of the person driving the tram##5
2. the owner of the goldfish is the person driving the tram##1
3. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
4. the owner of the fish is somewhere to the right of the owner of the hedgehog##5
5. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Pet   | hedgehog     | hamster | fish | goldfish |
| Transport     | helicopter | bike    | taxi    | tram |

