.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, milk, soy-milk
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, drama, time-travel, scientific
1. the person watching time-travel movies is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching scientific movies##5
3. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5
4. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere to the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
5. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
6. the person drinking cola is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person watching drama movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |       4       |
| Beverage      | milk     | soy-milk | cola     | hot-chocolate |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | scientific  | superhero | drama        |

