.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-19::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, surfing, rowing, handball
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, jet-ski, quad-bike, snowmobile
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is between the person driving the jet-ski and the person who's sport is surfing##2
2. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is handball##5
3. the person who's sport is rowing is somewhere to the left of the person driving the snowmobile##5
4. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
5. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Sport         | rowing   | handball   | lacrosse       | surfing   |
| Transport   | quad-bike | jet-ski | helicopter | snowmobile |

